      "time_str": "00:16.210",
      "text": "你的笑容是恩惠",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 23.58,
      "time_str": "00:23.580",
      "text": "世界难得那么美",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 29.15,
      "time_str": "00:29.150",
      "text": "于是追 要你陪",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 32.55,
      "time_str": "00:32.550",
      "text": "可惜本能终会将美丽汗水化成泪水",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.6,
      "time_str": "00:44.600",
      "text": "黑夜之所以会黑",
      "translation": null
